Package: heaven
Type: Package
Title: Data Preparation Routines for Medical Registry Data
Version: 2018.08.09
Author: Helene Charlotte Rytgaard, Anders Munch, Christian Torp-Pedersen, Jannik Pallisgaard, Regitze Kuhr Skals, Peter Enemark Lund, Thomas Alexander Gerds
Maintainer: Thomas A. Gerds <tag@biostat.ku.dk>
Description: Fast and furious implementations of often used data preparation steps.
             These functions are adapted to Danish registry data.
